3. Painite - 

 First discovered by English mineralogist Arthur C.D.  Pain in the 1950s in Myanmar, for many years, Painite has always been at the top of the list of the world's rarest gemstones with only 2 specimens found.


 Until 2005, scientists still found only 25 samples of Painite on the planet.  Therefore, the Guinness Book of Records recognized Painite as the most rare mineral in the world in 2005.

 Today, Painite is no longer as rare as it used to be.  It has been discovered a Painite mineral mine in Myanmar - where is considered the source of this stone.

 However, Painite is still on the list of the most precious minerals on Earth.  Therefore, the price of Painite is quite large - about..

[11/12/19, 9:59:40 AM] ‪+60 11‑2123 9822‬: NO UPFRONT PAYMENT!

If you are an end buyer for bg/sblc you can check if you are okay with this procedure ;

TRANSACTION PROCEDURES:
1. Buyer must submit documentation: Three options to verify POF/Proof of Funds  
A. Fully completed LOI and POF (Recent Bank statement or Tear sheet, BCL, or RWA see sample on page #11), and copies of two (2) bankers’ business cards.
 
B. Fully completed LOI and ATV (verify the funds via banker to banker), and copies of two bankers’ business cards.
 
C. The Buyer/Client contacts their banker(s) via email to request either a current screen shot and/or bank statement. The banker is to email their Client the requested information AND they are to Cc the Provider at secure email address.
 
2. Provider’s issuing banks compliance department(s) will contact the buyer’s bank to verify the cash or active line or credit / credit facility to begin the transaction.
 
3. Upon verification of financial capacity, provider will countersign the LOI, with full banking details, and the Provider’s banker will send a MT799 or MT199 Pre-advice.
 
4. Within 2 banking days, the buyer’s banker will respond with either a (MT799 BPU) or (MT199 RWA) stating they are ready to receive and pay for the MT760 SBLC.
 
5. Within 2 banking days, Provider’s banker will send the MT760 SBLC to the buyer’s banker.
 
6. Upon the SAME DAY Buyer’s banker will verifies MT760 SBLC, payment shall be immediately made with an Unconditional MT103 along with intermediaries’ commissions.
 
7. Hard Copy of the instrument will be delivered by Provider’s Banker via Bonded Courier to CLIENT bank within 7 banking days after receipt of the payment MT 103 by Provider’s bank

Note: This is just one of our procedures from one of our providers bg offers.

TRANSACTION PROCEDURES
 
1. RECEIVER submits to PROVIDER this signed Deed of Agreement (DOA), together with Client Information Sheet, (CIS), Corporate Board Resolution, Signatory’s Passport Copy, Corporate Registration and IMFPA.
 
2. PROVIDER countersigns the Deed of Agreement, which thereby automatically becomes a full recourse commercial contract and both Parties lodge the DOA with their respective Banks.
 
3. RECEIVER Bank will issue an MT 799 pre-advice / prove of funds to Provider Bank confirming that they are ready, Willing and Able to receive the SBLC.
 
4. PROVIDER’s Issuing Bank will issue an MT-799 Pre-Advice by SWIFT MT-799 (Exhibit A) confirming that they are Ready, Willing and Able to issue the STAND BY LETTER OF CREDIT (SBLC) as per agreed verbiage (Exhibit C).
 
5. Within Three (3) Banking days of receipt of Pre-advice MT-799 from the PROVIDER’S Bank, the RECEIVER’S Bank will send via SWIFT MT-799 a Bank Payment Undertaking (BPU - Exhibit B) for the amount due to Provider of XX% of the SBLC face value.
 
6. Within Two (2) Banking days of PROVIDER’S Bank’s receiving the BPU via SWIFT MT-799, PROVIDER’S Bank will deliver the STAND BY LETTER OF CREDIT via SWIFT MT-760 (Exhibit C).
 
7. On receipt, authentication and confirmation of the SBLC SWIFT MT-760, RECEIVER’S Bank effects the payment within Five (5) Banking days to PROVIDER’S nominated account by unconditional SWIFT  MT-103 and simultaneously pays 2% Consultancy fees as per details stated in the IMFPA.
 
8. Within Seven (7) Banking Days after receiving all payments, PROVIDER’S Bank will send the Hard copy of the SBLC to the RECEIVER’S Bank by Bank-bonded courier.
 
9. Transactions and their settlement will continue according to above-noted procedures and pre-agreed tranche schedule, until contracted collateral instruments are fully delivered.
 
Should RECEIVER default to pay the fees to the PROVIDER and commission to the Consultants as agreed in this DOA within the allowed number of days after receipt of SBLC via SWIFT-760 the PROVIDER shall instruct the Issuing Bank to put a claim on the SBLC thereby forcing the Receiver's Bank to return the SBLC to the issuing Bank
 
ALL SWIFT COPIES HAVE TO BE SENT TO THE OTHER PARTY WITHIN 24 HOURS FOR FOLLOWING UP AND TRACKING.
 
This Deed of Agreement is a full recourse commercial commitment governed by the Laws of the jurisdictions in which both Parties reside and subject to standards under ICC Regulations.
 
 
 
3. SANCTIONS (NON-PERFORMANCE)
 
After this contract is signed by both Sender and Receiver, and copies exchanged electronically or otherwise by a delivery service, failure to follow the closing procedures in time and form herein is considered breach of this contract that puts the failing party in default and under an obligation to pay a onetime penalty fee of 2% of the first tranche to the suffering Party.

Man is foolish.

Many are deceived to believe the whites are wise. I ask you, will any wise person manufacture weapons that destroys lives? Knowing fully well that if you kill you must be killed and whatever you do to others must surely be done unto you. 

Let our test be drawn from Everlasting Gospel vol. 2 Chapter 71 vs 148 to 158

"THERE IS NO DIFFERENCE BETWEEN MAN AND AN ANIMAL; THE BLOOD OF A GOAT FOR AN INSTANCE IS EXACTLY LIKE THE BLOOD OF A HUMAN BEING. 
Brethren, human beings deserve pity because for no reason should the blood of an animal enter into the mouth of a human being.

God gave man power to rule over the different kinds of animals and he is regarded as god to all other creatures of God. The proof is in the fact that no matter how huge an animal may be, as soon as it sees a man, it becomes weak and may fall down.
Brethren, know that you will be forgiven of whatever sin that you commit except that when you kill a man you will in turn be killed.
That was the more reason that our Lord Jesus Christ asked Peter to put back his sword into the sheath and added that he who takes the sword must die by the sword.

You are always deceived into thinking that the whites are wise but I ask, if this is so why should they manufacture destructive weapons? He who knows God commits no murder.
Many people allege that it is because of unemployment that they enrol as soldiers. I am assuring you that your eyes will open one day when you kill somebody even in the battlefield, for you will also be killed. 
Christ has known that whatever a person does to the other, the same will be done to him, hence He admonishes us to refrain from all manners of sins so that these sins may not stand against us.

We yearn for an everlasting life, yet we refuse to abide by the instructions of the Holy Spirit.How would we then have everlasting life and peace? 

Brethren, man is foolish. Note that if we refuse to abide by the directives of the Holy Spirit, there is nothing we can do to be saved.
YOU MAY CLING TO THE SAYING THAT YOU ARE SAVED BY GRACE, NOTE THAT YOU WERE SAVED BY GRACE SO THAT YOU MAY REFRAIN FROM SIN AND BE ABLE TO SERVE GOD WILLINGLY, what shall we say then? Shall we continue in sin, that grace may abound? ".

A man once told me he has been practicing righteousness all his life during my gospel and when asked if he has not been eating meat and fish these years, he kept quiet.Then later said he didn't know it's unrighteous.

Two sisters were fighting over a meat and when asked what's the problem, one said the other should give her back her meat. When asked "her meat"? She thought over it and walked away without any more word.. Why? Because she imagined what she just said and probably pondered over what if it was actually her flesh that was being dragged.

When one isn't conscious enough to realise he is not being nice to God, to humanity or himself by killing or patronising killers how would he know what is good for his neighbor ?
People should stop arrogating their problems to their neighbors and love one another because the problems are caused by stubbornness and unrepentance from sin.

Let those who have ears hear.

 और दुनिया की पहली बड़े पैमाने पर उत्पादित असिंक्रोनस मोटर्स जिसमें स्लावंका प्रकार की संयुक्त वाइंडिंग्स हैं, प्रदर्शन IP65 के 100 वें आयाम की कर्षण मोटरें होंगी।  उनके बीयरिंगों को विशेष तेल सील के साथ कवर किया जाएगा, जो धूल, गंदगी और नमी को संरचना में प्रवेश करने से रोकता है।  ऐसे मोटर्स अधिक बहुमुखी और मांग में हैं।
 इंजन पहले से ही EAEU द्वारा प्रमाणन के लिए तैयार किए जा रहे हैं, जिससे उन्हें रूस के बाहर बेचना संभव होगा।  निकट भविष्य में, सोफ़्टलेश वेबसाइट पर ट्रैक्शन मोटर्स की विस्तृत जानकारी दिखाई देगी और एक प्री-ऑर्डर सेक्शन बनाया गया है।

 इंजनों का पहला बैच एक बड़े औद्योगिक उद्यम के लिए है, जो अपने उत्पादन के वाहनों पर ड्यूयुनोव इंजन स्थापित करेगा।  इंजन की स्थापना और कमीशनिंग में मदद करने के लिए दो उद्यमशील कर्मचारी इस उद्यम के काम में शामिल होंगे।  पहले से ही इस साल के मई में, स्लाव्यंका के साथ मोटर वाला एक उत्पाद परिवहन प्रदर्शनी में जाएगा।
 पहले बैच से इंजन का एक हिस्सा परियोजना में कई लोगों को अच्छी तरह से जाना जाता है।  उनके नाम, साथ ही औद्योगिक उद्यम के नाम का खुलासा बाद में किया जाएगा, जबकि यह एक व्यापार रहस्य है।

 मैं जोर देना चाहता हूं कि दिमित्री ड्यूयुनोव की टीम प्रतिकूल परिस्थितियों के बावजूद भी अपनी बात रखती है!  परियोजना की शुरुआत में, यह वादा किया गया था कि 3 साल में सोएवलेश में पहले इंजन का उत्पादन शुरू किया जाएगा।  अब कंपनी वादा पूरा करने के करीब है, उद्यम के सभी बलों और क्षमताओं को अब योजना के कार्यान्वयन के लिए फेंक दिया गया है।

 नवाचार केंद्र सोवएलैश की परियोजना की राज्य परीक्षा पास करने के बारे में खबर है।  वे उन कमियों को खत्म करने के लिए काम पूरा करने के करीब हैं जिनके लिए टिप्पणियां की गई थीं, आयोग द्वारा अतिरिक्त सामग्री का अनुरोध किया जा रहा है।  परियोजना के उन वर्गों के लिए जहां से टिप्पणियां वापस ली गई थीं, राज्य परीक्षा की समाप्ति के बाद समय बर्बाद किए बिना, उन्हें जांचने के लिए सोवलेश कर्मचारियों ने अनुमानों को उतार दिया।

[5/16/20, 3:19:32 AM] ‪+91 86307 40563‬: EASY CLUB SMART CONTRACT

* 'ब्लॉकचैन स्मार्ट कॉन्ट्रैक्ट' एक Decentralized सिस्टम है, आइये कुछ जानकारी शेयर करते है मित्रो..😊*

Smart Contract Decentralized system kya hai ??

👉 स्मार्ट कॉन्ट्रैक्ट एक प्रोग्रामिंग है, जिसको एथेरियम के ब्लॉकचैन में रन कराया जाता है।

👉यह एक सच्चाई है ब्लॉकचैन की बिस्वस्नियता पर आज तक कोई भी उंगली नहीं उठा सकता है !

👉 प्रोग्रामिंग को बनाने वाला ब्लॉकचैन में डालने से पहले इस कोडिंग में कुछ भी बदलाव कर सकता है, लेकिन जैसे ही वो अपने प्रोग्राम को ब्लॉकचैन में डाल देता है उसके बाद वो चाह के भी कुछ नही कर सकता।

👉 वो ना कोई एडिट कर सकता है, ना ब्लॉक कर सकता है ना वापिस ले सकता है।

👉 यानी अब जो भी करेगा सिर्फ ब्लॉकचैन ही करेगा, इस लिए इसको Decentralized सिस्टम कहते है।

👉 जब तक पूरे विश्व में इंटरनेट है, तब तक ब्लॉकचैन है, और जब तक ब्लॉकचैन है तब तक वो प्रोग्रामिंग (कांसेप्ट) है।

*अब सवाल ये आता है कि Centralized & Decentralized में क्या फर्क है मित्रो.??*😀

👉 Centralized सिस्टम का मतलब है कि उसका कोई मालिक (एडमिन) हैं. आब्जर्वर जब चाहे अपने प्लान को बंद कर सकता है, एडिट कर सकता है, किसी की user id को ब्लॉक भी कर सकता है या वेबसाइट बन्द करके सारा पैसा हज़म करके फरार भी हो सकता है।

👉 Decentralized सिस्टम का मतलब ये है, कि उसको कोई बन्द नही कर सकता कभी भी, एडिट नही कर सकता और वो पैसा लेकर फरार भी नही हो सकता !

👉 आज मार्केट में जब भी हम कोई भी सिस्टम बताते हैं, तो सबसे पहला सवाल लोग यही पूछते है कि प्लान कब तक चलेगा और हम लोग उसको गोल-गोल जवाब देते है. क्योंकिं हकीकत यही की कोई भी सिस्टम कब तक चलेगा ये हमे भी पता नही होता था।

👉 इसलिए अब आप कोई भी सिस्टम कीजिये जों Decentralized ही हों मित्रो जिससे आपलोग का फेस वैल्यू खराब ना हो और आप अपने टीम के साथ कई कई वर्षो तक कॉन्फिडेंस से काम कर सके ।

👉ब्लॉकचैन स्मार्ट कॉन्ट्रेक्ट हमें धौकेबाज एडमिन, लालची लीडर्स, फैक अकाउंट आदि से बचाता है, औऱ हमारे पैसे की सुरक्षा करता रहता है!

👉सिस्टम ब्लॉकचैन स्मार्ट कॉन्ट्रेक्ट पर बना होने के कारण सिस्टम Decentralized है (जेसे कि बिटकॉइन etc.)
Program is transparent and all Ethereum collected can be viewed in the Etherscan blockchain wallet 
https://etherscan.io/address/0x98AD263a95F1ab1AbFF41F4D44b07c3240251A0a
From here you can see the health and progress if the program
